Agree to never reprint any article from this site via any unsolicited email, spamming, or pop up ads
Agree to never sell any article from Intomillion or associated sites
Agree to not add any active links to any article you reprint from Intomillion site as this could lead someone
to believe falsely that the author of the article endorses the active link which is not the case
Agree to never translate any content from Intomillion site in any language or into derivative works without permission which may be sought by contacts